{
  "stem": "1860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 76.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this way, she-- she was able to save it for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- the most drastic change-- well, my father left, my brother left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was already break up of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the schools were closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I realized we had financial problems we-- to-- to-- to support ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And thanks to this cousin Banker, we-- we managed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We managed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And then, of course, came the-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] they were forming the ghetto [INAUDIBLE] outskirts of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But not everybody was fortunate to be allowed to get to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You needed a so-called [NON-ENGLISH], identity card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't get one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to leave Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I can recall, you had to either work for certain-- in certain workplaces in order to-- to be entitled to-- to get it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And anyway, we-- we couldn't get to ghetto, so we left the apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We packed up whatever we could into a few valises, and we went to a small town called Wolbrom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our-- my mother's uncle lived there already who also was resettled from a different town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we felt we might as well be somewhere where we-- where we have some relatives.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came to Wolbrom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We lived there in one room with kitchen privileges.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when we were packing to go to Wolbrom, as long as I remember, just so happened that my mother was very sick.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had an infection in her leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was high fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was the one who was in charge of packing and deciding what-- what goes, what-- what stays.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I imagine, because I was young, I still had some hopes.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
